transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello, Namaskar sir. 
Customer: Haanji. Main ye bol raha tha sir ki domain ka access ke liye mail ID aur password aapne jisse wo login karana domain. 
Executive: Basically wo chahiye honge. 
Customer: Matlab basically jo mail ID aur password, user ID aur password honge na domain ke wo chahiye honge. Uske baad hi access hoga. 
Executive: Achcha. 
Customer: Uske baad hi hum apne access kar payenge. Matlab jaise maine GoDaddy se purchase kiya hai to aapko uska ID password chahiye aisa bol rahe hain aap? 
Executive: GoDaddy se aapne purchase kiya hai aap uska de do main GoDaddy ka de do. 
Customer: Hai na to aap mujhe aap mujhe email pe likh ke bhej dijiye ki aapko GoDaddy ka account ka ID and password chahiye to main aapko bhejta hun. 
Executive: Okay, okay main aapko mail kar deta hun. 
Customer: Haan. Mail ID sir ek baar confirm karenge aap apna? 
Executive: Haan. Aapke paas kaun sa hai? 
Customer: Ek minute main bata deta hun. 
Executive: Mere paas jo show kar raha hai sir wo simply S ke baad teen star and S matlab S se start hota hai @omega rubber.com. Basically hume itna hi show kar raha hai. 
Customer: Achcha. 
Executive: S se start ho raha hai basically S se start ho raha hai actually usme bhi do hai S se jo chalu hote hain. Mostly sales@omegarubber hoga, theek hai. 
Customer: To aap usi pe mail dijiye jispe aapke jispe aapke paas access hai main dekh lunga. 
Executive: Okay.
Customer: Haanji. Haan.
